Who needs a complicated routine when 2 steps does the absolute most? 

I start the day with the @icosmetiques Total Care Face Wash Powder! 

This innovative cleanser comes in a dry powder form that transforms into a rich, creamy lather with just a few drops of water. 💦 
It’s super gentle but powerfully effective — infused with pure Vitamin C + E! 🍊🧪

Why powder? Because it keeps Pure Vitamin C stable and potent — max glow + antioxidant power every time. 🙌

I follow it up with the @icosmetiques Advance Care Age Defying Serum — a lightweight, collagen-boosting formula that firms, smooths, and visibly reduces premature signs of aging. 💧

Clean. Effective. Proven. 

This duo = glowing skin made simple. 🤍
